From b36b047b94d22050d3a06f4e5c9a143dc8029150 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Michael Glembotzki <Michael.Glembotzki@iris-sensing.com>
Date: Tue, 26 May 2026 14:34:25 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Update Mongoose with security fixes
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Source: Cesanta proactive security alert, 22 May 2026

Vulnerabilities summary (59 issues):

mqtt server stack overflow
mqtt_next_topic OOB
Remote Denial of Service (Infinite Loop) via Integer Overflow in Built-in TLS DER Parser
Built-in TLS accepts non-CA certificates as issuing intermediates
ETH L2 footer
aes gcm no tag verify
tcp option infinite loop
mg_http_get_header_var OOB Read
RSA Zero-Length Modulus OOB Read
X25519 Low-Order Point Unchecked
ICMPv6 NDP NA OOB Read
Multipart Boundary/Header Scan Logic Error Causes Data Corruption and Content-Type Bypass
HTTP/1.0 Detection Off-by-One Enables Request Smuggling
SSI Path Traversal â€” Arbitrary File Read via `#include` Directives
Stored XSS via Unescaped Filenames in Directory Listing
opendir stack overflow via wcscat on MAX_PATH path
mg_tcpip_driver_tms570_tx short frames transmit stale buffer contents
ENET_IRQHandler RX descriptor not re-owned on error -- RX ring stall
ssl_keylog_cb NULL deref on fopen failure
ff_open missing f_close on allocation failure leaks FatFs lock
mg_file_write temp file opened without O_EXCL -- symlink following
mg_file_write temp name truncation causes original file deletion
w5100_rx wraparound RX path copies n instead of r bytes
cyw_spi_tx SPI alignment padding indexes uint32_t* buffer with byte offset
mg_getlocaddr socket leaked on UDP connect() failure
rx_ip truncated DHCP options size_t underflow OOB read
rx_dhcp_client 32-bit overflow in DHCP lease millisecond conversion
ppp_rx fixed-size hexdump OOB read on short unknown-protocol frame
ppp_handle_ipcp attacker-controlled IPCP length -- OOB read
find_opt zero-length PPP option -- infinite loop
rx_ndp_na NDP NA missing option length check -- OOB read
rx_ndp_ns ICMPv6 NS minimum length insufficient -- OOB read
rx_ip6 IPv6 extension header OOB read; 16-bit len wrap
NDP RA allows any value for MTU
mg_ssi 1-byte OOB stack read in SSI end-of-tag check
mg_ssi iobuf buffer leaked on allocation failure
DNS transaction ID is sequential -- enables response injection
MQTT v5 properties bounds check uses relative offset against absolute position
skip_chunk off-by-one OOB read in chunked HTTP CRLF check
mg_rsa_parse_key OOB read in debug logging before bounds check
gcm_finish unbounded tag_len OOB read
mg_dtoa stack overflow appending exponent suffix
precompute_slide_window NULL deref on OOM
more_comps NULL deref after failed calloc
bi_initialize / alloc NULL deref on OOM
mg_tls_client_recv_hello size_t underflow in ext_len bounds check
mg_tls_client_recv_hello ext_len fixed-offset OOB read
mg_tls_server_recv_hello session_id_len OOB read
mg_tls_init EC key corruption via missing return + memory leak on error paths
mg_tls_client_recv_hello key_share extension OOB read
mg_tls_verify_cert_signature OOB read for short ECDSA integers
mg_tls_parse_cert_der pubkey BIT STRING length underflow -- OOB read
mg_der_to_tlv long-form DER length OOB read
mg_der_find_oid unbounded recursion on constructed DER tags
mg_tls_recv_cert certificate chain length unchecked -- OOB read
mg_random rand() fallback used for TLS secrets
ClientHello transmitted after RNG failure with rand()-derived key material
TLS certificate notAfter validated against hardcoded 2025-01-01 string
RSA-PSS CertificateVerify checks only 0xbc trailer

Signed-off-by: Michael Glembotzki <Michael.Glembotzki@iris-sensing.com>
